1. *Muškarce* su obučeni u svečane odore. (Men are dressed in formal wear.)
2. *Muškarci* su sa nama išli na izlet. (The men went on a trip with us.)
3. *Muškarcima* je bilo najteže da sve pripreme. (It was hardest for the men to prepare everything.)
4. *Muškaraca* je bilo pet na događaju. (There were five men at the event.)
5. *Muškarci* su se zabavljali na proslavi. (The men were having fun at the celebration.)